{"tid":1633898,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE娜璉被誤會划水一年 親口解答「《YES or YES》第二段編舞」不跳原因","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T05:33:13.000Z","uid":74065,"like":11,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"792d3824c11ece1a5ad9865072165af3496a6c0f","tid":1633898,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE成員娜璉是隊中大姐，但是可愛的行為和個性常常讓人有「忙內」（老么）的錯覺。不過自從去年發行《YES or YES》以來，她常常被質疑「為什麼第二段編舞不跳」，甚至有人攻擊娜璉「划水」（意指不認真跳舞）。她也透過直播說清楚答案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4418/d4418731.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4418%2Fd4418731.jpg&h=190ffa55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE娜璉解釋《YES or YES》「為什麼第二段編舞不跳」的原因。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<br />\n娜璉日前在直播上，對於常常聽到的「為什麼《YES or YES》第二段編舞不跳」的問題直接解答。娜璉透露，確實很常聽到這樣的疑問，「為什麼志效的Part不做手部動作？」她解釋道：「想說一下只有我不做的原因，理由就是，因為怕志效被擋住。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4418/d4418724.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4418%2Fd4418724.gif&h=2f46613a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE娜璉，是為了不要擋住志效。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n一句話終於解決一年來許多粉絲甚至黑粉的疑問，因為娜璉也曾因為這點被網友惡意攻擊「划水」。理由公開後，不少粉絲說：「人美又善良，卻被一些人誤會了這麼久。」為偶像感到心疼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4418/d4418733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4418%2Fd4418733.jpg&h=5b2afd28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE娜璉，是為了不要擋住志效。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<br />\n過去娜璉也因舞台上經常跌跌撞撞站不穩，有粉絲問本人「為何腳這麼沒力？」娜璉也親口回覆：「小時候因為出過車禍，受了很嚴重的傷」，並表示當時受傷的左腳比較沒力，「現在能走路真的很感激。」這段對話在網路上公開後，許多人表示「現在看到她跌倒都不覺得好笑了」、「事實讓人嚇了一跳」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人信??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdfe9999eb9a42b361dc4c5c9449bf17aa52b73","tid":1633898,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528461834debfa3b2586c9391267778fd52af3cf","tid":1633898,"uid":111517,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"咸左😭<br />\n原來娜璉一直feel special志效😭"},{"pid":"51205d8f9d2dc5d949a5517ea8d1c39798e689d9","tid":1633898,"uid":138138,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:50:13.000Z","msg":"人美又善良，卻被一些人誤會了這麼久。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7521785b5f8b26bdbdb787e480b5f10de2d59211","tid":1633898,"uid":238483,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:51:31.000Z","msg":"比某黑警會員屈左咁耐<br />\n依家終於沉冤得雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f00198d4410d02604a8c3cd3b5164f66583ef3","tid":1633898,"uid":208486,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:51:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我保護她💘✊<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZ10Wdk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZ10Wdk.jpg&h=a9cfb493&s={SIZE}\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a6de2451e3427cd6c2a6439b96086ee6a87eab65","tid":1633898,"uid":87394,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"呢個答案諗左成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e504f4dcdb32dbdd75213a9992096f9aa5c188","tid":1633898,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"三歲暖能到..😭😭"},{"pid":"47c341f8c7a8deb839537907c6e6d82e1e6cecbd","tid":1633898,"uid":76115,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:58: